{"tid":1055430,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[NBA] 瘋狂奶死沾狗袋底同學會討論區 (1)","createTime":"2019-03-10T14:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T09:29:32.000Z","uid":151333,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cfab599db079030f52c9398fb9d9757a02f96de9","tid":1055430,"uid":151333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:12:49.000Z","msg":"今年為左自己事業，家人選擇左去LA<br />\n季初還算順風順水，而且新陣營仲未打出完全夾好，仲有d球員未傷好都打出咁既表現實在充滿期待<br />\n但不幸地年尾遇上一次大傷，缺席左一段時間，湖人無人支撐到隊波，而且rondo同ball都分別傷埋<br />\n及後仲要遇上吹左幾個星期既ad trade搞到軍心重傷<br />\n<br />\n雖然...今年都算係佢人生中一大個里程碑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4L5KG5h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4L5KG5h.png&h=df43a2cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但....湖人已經可以肯定入唔到playoff...<br />\n一個playoff無左lbj真係好唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />莫講話finals<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家去點平衡自己去面對/睇今年既playoff<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會去睇其他隊，定龜縮幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定直頭引退唔睇NBA了？睇近十場波，感覺lbj已經唔係打得起了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca744605fbf3fdb277ce07bd78add03d7a05490a","tid":1055430,"uid":151333,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:19:30.000Z","msg":"矛人理，入黎笑下班/個垃圾fans啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0a70ca6c24382cc4f6b2d6bb79efb48fc3af75","tid":1055430,"uid":151333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5640fdaab79d6ca5612bd5a574142a69f05cbc37","tid":1055430,"uid":151333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T00:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349bc4a7233863fcfe746a7b01